import pandas as pd
# Load the dataset
adult_df = pd.read_csv('source_files/Adult.csv')
# Calculate the frequency of each bin
bins = [0, 20, 40, 60, 80, 100]
adult_df['hours-per-week_binned'] = pd.cut(adult_df['hours-per-week'], bins=bins)
freqs = adult_df['hours-per-week_binned'].value_counts(normalize=True)
# Determine the maximum and minimum bin frequencies
max_freq = freqs.max()
min_freq = freqs.min()
# Calculate the max/min ratio
max_min_ratio = max_freq / min_freq
print('Max/Min Ratio:', max_min_ratio)
